   <text:p text:style-name="P25">Perdiccas — numele mai multor regi aiMacedoniei : Perdiccas 1 (sec. VII î.e.n.), Perdiccas al II-lea (450—c, 413 î.e.n.), Perdiccas al. III-lea (365—359 i.e.n.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P25"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P25">Perdiccas (?2—32] î.e.n.) — general macedonean, proclamat regent la moartea lui Alexandru Macedon.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P25"/>
